title: Railworks TS2014 RailTraction BR 628-2
description:
Diesel Multiple Unit (DMU) BR 628-2

Quick drive compatible.

There are two scenarios included:
BR628-2 - Destination Lindau (Three Country Corner Route)
BR628-2 - Regio Service (Hamburg - Hanover)
